1. Nalazimo se u dve različite *grupe* (We are in two different groups).

2. Oni su članovi različitih *grupa* (They are members of different groups).

3. Naša *grupa* čini pet ljudi (Our group consists of five people).

4. *Grupe* su napravile različite aktivnosti (The groups did different activities).

5. Oni su se podelili u dve *grupe* (They divided into two groups).

6. *Grupa* je bila veoma zadovoljna sa rezultatima (The group was very satisfied with the results).